<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>会員登録 - Gourmet Life</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/reset.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/account.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <%- include('partials/header.ejs', { currentPath: currentPath }) %>

        <main>
            <form action="/signup" method="POST">

                <h1 class="main-title">会員登録</h1>

                <div class="account-form">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="username">ユーザ名</label>
                        <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">メールアドレス</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="password">パスワード</label>
                        <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="confirm-password">パスワード再入力</label>
                        <input type="password" id="confirm-password" name="confirm_password" required>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr>

                <div class="terms">
                    <h2>利用規約</h2>
                    <div class="terms-content">
                        <p>ユーザーは以下の規約に同意する必要があります。</p>
                        <p>
                            規約<br>規約<br>規約<br>規約<br>規約<br>規約<br>規約<br>規約<br>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="agree-checkbox" class="form-group agree">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="agree" name="agree" required>
                    <label for="agree">利用規約に同意します。</label>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group agree">
                    <button class="account-btn" type="submit">確認画面へ</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </main>

        <%- include('../views/partials/footer.ejs') %>
    </div>
</body>

</html>